An inspiring and refined design that has ensured Natalia's coveted status. It's a triumph in understated glamour, petite with a modern handwriting, featuring a shorter top handle. Named after the International model and philanthropist Natalia Vodianova, it radiates poise.

* Top handle

* Gold-plated rope logo lock

* Matching handle fittings

* Extra-long shoulder strap

* Back pocket

* Interior pocket

* Inner zip

* Suede-lined

* Leather-covered mirror

Size: Length 17cm x Height 15cm (22cm inc/handle) x Depth 6.5cm

Upon checkout, this handbag will be made by our skilled craftspeople in a process that takes up to ⁨3–4 weeks⁩. You will be notified via email through each step of the production and delivery process. Delivery to ⁨United Kingdom⁩ is carried out by our shipping partners and can take an additional ⁨3 days⁩⁨⁩. Further details are available on our delivery information page. Returns can be accepted within 15 days of delivery provided no customisations have been applied to the product.
